msgid "We're a group of builders who believe scaling your app shouldn't kill your creativity. We've experienced the frustration of watching exciting Swift projects turn into build-time nightmares and tooling headaches as they grow, so we decided to build something better."
msgstr "我哋係一班建造者，相信擴展應用唔應該扼殺創意。我哋親歷睇住精彩嘅 Swift 項目成长過程中變成建置惡夢同工具麻煩，決定打造更好嘅解決方案。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/support.html.heex:9
